&lt;p&gt;This is primarily a hands-on engineering role with a technical leadership component. You will spend most of your time writing code, designing systems, and solving engineering problems, while also mentoring a small team and driving platform direction. The ideal candidate is a strong Java backend engineer comfortable working across the full stack, with a platform-ownership mindset - from code to production.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform Ownership: &lt;/strong&gt;Own the Ticketing platform end-to-end — architecture, development, deployment, and production operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Backend &amp;amp; Full-Stack Development: &lt;/strong&gt;Build and maintain production-grade Java services, work with SQL Server for query optimization and schema migrations, and contribute to frontend changes when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DevOps &amp;amp; Cloud: &lt;/strong&gt;Own CI/CD pipelines (Git, Maven/Gradle, GitLab CI) and manage containerized deployments on AWS (ECS, RDS, S3, CloudWatch).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Observability &amp;amp; Incident Response: &lt;/strong&gt;Build monitoring dashboards and alerting. Lead incident response, root cause analysis, and post-mortems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security: &lt;/strong&gt;Ensure platform security — authentication, authorization, secrets management, cross-client isolation, and annual security upgrades.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Leadership: &lt;/strong&gt;Mentor and guide engineers through code reviews, design discussions, and technical direction. Coordinate with cross-functional stakeholders on delivery and roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation: &lt;/strong&gt;Maintain technical documentation, runbooks, and architecture decision records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Need&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Backend Engineering — Java: &lt;/strong&gt;Strong expertise in Java including concurrency, collections, streams, and JVM internals. Comfortable working with vendor or legacy codebases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SQL Server: &lt;/strong&gt;Hands-on experience with query optimization, schema migrations (Liquibase), connection pool management, and performance monitoring.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full-Stack Capability: &lt;/strong&gt;Proficiency in JavaScript and modern UI

