&lt;p&gt;The Principal, Client Delivery &amp;amp; Implementations owns the end-to-end success of one or more concurrent Arcesium implementation projects for institutional clients. This is a client-leadership role that requires the judgment to navigate complex organizational environments, the credibility to partner with senior stakeholders, and the discipline to drive outcomes when competing priorities and structural complexity create headwinds.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
